4. Competitive Differentiators (Supplements)

vs. Cheap Amazon Brands
	•	Clinically studied ingredients
	•	Higher purity
	•	Transparent sourcing
	•	Real dosages (not fairy dust formulas)

vs. Big Box Retail Brands
	•	Cleaner ingredients
	•	No fillers or junk
	•	Higher absorption
	•	Modern, research-backed formulations

vs. Other Premium DTC Brands
	•	Better price per serving
	•	More transparent sourcing
	•	Higher dosages
	•	Stronger customer results and reviews

